    <h1 class="hidden">
        Global Careers - Canada Line of Business</h1>
    <table summary="Global Careers - Canada Line of Business" width="366" border="0"
        cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
        <tr>
            <td width="366" align="left" valign="top">
                <p>
                    Bank of America partners with the following Lines of Business to provide financial
                    products and services throughout Canada:</p>
                <h2>
                    Canada Card Services</h2>
                <p>
                    Bank of America has different areas in the bank that handle incoming and outgoing
                    calls as well as responding to customer mail. These customer contact areas are:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Fraud</li><li>Credit</li><li>Collections</li><li>Customer Marketing</li><li>Customer
                        Service</li><li>Resolution services</li></ul>
                <p>
                    Other areas under Card Services include-Risk strategies, Business Development, and
                    Marketing.</p>
                <h2>
                    Global HR</h2>
                <p>
                    Global Human Resources covers a wide range of areas including Payroll, Benefits,
                    Retirement, Communications, Compensation, Staffing, HR Consultants, and Associate
                    Experience. The main goal is to support and guide all associates with questions
                    about their career and other important concerns that impact them both personally
                    and professionally. We also focus on reward and recognition programs which recognize
                    those who go above and beyond in their positions.</p>
                <h2>
                    Legal</h2>
                <p>
                    Bank of America's Legal Services supports the Canadian Lines of Business and Support
                    Partners in meeting their key objectives.&nbsp; Legal services manage legal and
                    regulatory risks for the bank by identifying and mitigating&nbsp;these risks.&nbsp;
                    We&nbsp;also provide education with respect to ongoing and emerging legal issues,
                    and assist with governance and reporting requirements.</p>
                <h2>
                    Finance</h2>
                <p>
                    The Finance Department is team of professionals, dedicated to maximizing the company&rsquo;s
                    growth and profitability, while maintaining best-in-class asset control and balance
                    sheet management. Our mission is to provide sustainable, high value influence and
                    direction for key business decisions and actions, as well as provide effective controls
                    to ensure satisfactory internal and external audit reviews.&nbsp; The Department
                    manages these goals through the following functions: Planning and Management Reporting,
                    Profitability and Data Analysis, Accounts Payable, General Ledger/Accounting, Settlement,
                    Reconciliation, Regulatory Reporting, and Financial Applications support</p>
                <h2>
                    Learning and Leadership Development</h2>
                <p>
                    Learning &amp; Leadership Development is a team of professionals, dedicated to driving
                    the company's growth through providing our business partners with unsurpassed expertise
                    to meet these top priorities:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Build depth and versatility in our bench </li>
                    <li>Improve the quality and impact of talent assessments </li>
                    <li>Implement a reliable and flexible global learning infrastructure </li>
                    <li>Revamp and integrate leadership development programs </li>
                    <li>Achieve in-year hard-dollar productivity targets and establish 2008 opportunities
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <p>
                    Additionally, Learning and Leadership Development is applying some of these priorities
                    to our own organization to continue to drive associate engagement and commitment,
                    which is of paramount importance to our satisfaction and our success</p>
                <br />
                <br />
            </td>
        </tr>
